  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Jammu & Kashmir</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Jammu & Kashmir experiences extreme seasonal variations. Summer (May-August) offers pleasant weather in Kashmir valley, autumn (September-October) brings crisp air and clear skies, winter (December-February) transforms valleys into snow wonderlands. Ladakh has short summer season (June-September). Each season offers unique experiences.</p>
